{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "14", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "13", "M": "24", "S": "15"}}, "news": [{"title": "\u2018No power of review\u2019: Bombay HC nixes deemed conveyance to housing society", "para": "The Bombay High Court has quashed a deemed conveyance order, stating the competent authority lacked the power to entertain a second application on a finalized issue. Justice Farhan Dubash ruled the deputy registrar exercised an unrecognized review power, barring the second application by principles of finality and res judicata.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/bombay-hc-overturns-deemed-conveyance-for-andheri-housing-society-a-verdict-on-legal-finality/131716219?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-216822/131716219.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Odisha government to introduce new act soon as it plans major shift in urban rental housing", "para": "Odisha is set to introduce the draft Odisha Urban Area Rent Control Act, 2026, replacing the 1967 act. The legislation mandates written agreements, caps security deposits, and establishes rent authorities and courts for speedy dispute resolution, aiming to balance tenant and landlord rights.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/odisha-to-revamp-urban-rental-housing-with-new-rent-control-act/131716191?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-154374/131716191.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Panchkula civic body to discuss property tax waiver in its first General House meeting", "para": "Panchkula's first General House meeting on June 16 will focus on key development agendas, including making Ward No. 4 a model cleanliness ward and implementing a property tax amnesty to recover \u20b9100 crore in dues. The meeting will also address civic infrastructure upgrades, waterlogging solutions, and broader development goals like recreation centers and sports facilities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/panchkula-municipal-corporation-to-discuss-major-property-tax-waiver-and-cleanliness-initiatives-in-upcoming-meeting/131716148?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-95998/131716148.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}